Not reliable.
Not trustworthy.

28
00:02:30,638 --> 00:02:32,555
Can't stand up to the White House.

29
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,710
Backstabbers.

30
00:02:34,734 --> 00:02:36,788
Watching porn, tapping phones.

31
00:02:38,495 --> 00:02:39,902
What is his name?

32
