I doubt that, sir.

75
00:08:22,663 --> 00:08:25,556
I have skills
better deployed in the field.

76
00:08:44,118 --> 00:08:45,418
Come in.

77
00:08:47,825 --> 00:08:49,125
Milt.

78
00:08:49,214 --> 00:08:50,601
Wanna grab lunch?

79
